        <updateDate>2020-04-06T19:06:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Interim Stay Authority To Protect Whistleblowers Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the general counsel of the Merit Systems Protection Board to temporarily act as a member of the board when dealing with matters related to the staying of certain personnel actions, and it authorizes a single member of the board to carry out certain board duties in the event of a lack of quorum. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
